features: EXCITING 2-IN-1 TRANSFORMERS TOY: This Prowl action figure converts from robot mode to police car mode! The easy Transformers conversion is fun for kids ages 6 and up
CONVERTS BETWEEN MODES IN 12 STEPS: This interactive toy can change from a robot toy into a police car toy in 12 steps. Kids who love fidget toys will love the satisfying conversion!
5-INCH ROBOT ACTION FIGURE: In robot mode, Prowl figure is 5 inches (12.5 cm) tall
POLICE CAR MODE: Imagine epic battle scenes with Prowl in police car mode! Wheels really roll for storytelling fun. Great for kids who love toy cars
2 ACCESSORIES: This robot toy comes with 2 turbo booster flame accessory pieces that can be attached in both modes
TRANSFORMERS: EARTHSPARK CHARACTERS: Inspired by the loyal Autobot strategist, Prowl, from the Transformers: EarthSpark animated series
TRANSFORMERS ACTION FIGURES FOR BOYS AND GIRLS 6 AND UP: Transformers toys like the Deluxe Class Prowl make great gifts for boys and girls who love robot toys
body.description: The Transformers: EarthSpark Prowl Deluxe Class figure converts from robot to police car mode in 12 steps! Fans of the animated series will love imagining epic battles with this 5-inch Prowl figure in robot mode, then changing it into a toy car and zooming along to save the day! 2-in-1 Prowl toy also comes with 2 turbo booster flame accessories that can be attached in robot or vehicle mode. Look for more Deluxe Class Transformers figures (each sold separately, subject to availability) featuring popular characters from the Transformers: Earthspark show, an animated series that centers on two human kids as they forge a connection with Transformers robots like never before and work alongside fan favorites like Optimus Prime and Bumblebee! Interactive toys like the Deluxe Class Prowl make cool gifts for boys and girls ages 6 and up. Transformers and all related characters are trademarks of Hasbro.
